    <object name="player">
      <inherit name="defaultplayer" />
    </object>
    <object name="firstparttalk">
      <inherit name="scripttext" />
      <script type="script">
        SetForegroundColour ("Red")
        msg ("Foc: You went quite out of your way to stop Abigail's death, however you can't truly stop a death.")
        msg ("Foc: Everyone has to pass eventually and every time someone prevents that they just barely buy themselves some extra time.")
        msg ("Foc: In your pointless efforts you caused quite some deaths.")
        msg ("Foc: I hear you say that those people were not real, but neither is Abigail. The only difference is that she has more dialogue.")
        msg ("Foc: Even if we ignore all the other people that didn't have to die we still have Abigail. Granted, you saved her countless times but you also made her suffer more deaths than the average human has to go through.")
        msg ("Foc: And look where all of this amounted to, now all of reality is collapsing in on itself.")
        msg ("Foc: To them this is reality at the very least.")
        msg ("Foc: I was created by the creator of this world, of this game so to speak.")
        msg ("Foc: The only reason I was made was to dispose this endless onslaught of dialogue to you, the player.")
        msg ("Foc:  Because the maker of all of this was sure that if one path ended up here there would atleast be one person to come here.")
        msg ("Foc: Seeing you here, I suppose he was right.")
        msg ("Foc : I wonder what made you come here. Was it the chance that you could save Abigail or was it just merely to see what would be happening on this path? Perhaps it is better to leave that question unanswered for now.")
        msg ("Foc: I think I'm finished, and that's because the part of me that is the creator says so in the dialogue, although I suppose I made it more of a monologue didn't I?")
        msg ("Foc : I wasn't here before you walked this path and when you leave it I won't be here either, so this is my goodbye to you...")
        msg ("Foc: I petty you, I had a nice time meeting you but I hope that you'll never be tempted to walk this path again. May we never meet again and goodbye.")
        msg ("Foc: Also, a little advice, if you seek to set your mistake right then go to the place were three became one.")
        AddPageLink (firstparttalk, Page1, "Retry")
        SetFlagOff ("firsttalk")
        SetFlagOn ("twotalk")
        RemovePageLink (Weneedtotalkplayertocreator, firstparttalk)
      </script>
    </object>
  </object>
